tel-aviv/0000018e-9041-def1-a58f-f47909760000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 176 天：以色列国防军称哈马斯高级成员在 Al-Shifa 医院行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-176-idf-says-senior-hamas-members-killed-in-al-shifa-operation/0000018e-9055-d9a4-a7bf-dc5d1d7c0000</link><description>以色列国防军：三名哈马斯高级成员在 Al-Shifa 袭击中丧生 ■ 以色列推动建立多国部队以确保援助交付 ■ 四名联合国工作人员在黎巴嫩南部受伤；以色列国防军否认参与其中 ■ 以色列国防军在 13 岁巴勒斯坦人被军队枪杀后展开调查 ■ 据称以色列周五对叙利亚发动袭击，导致 52 人死亡 ■ 战争结束 176 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 17:28:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-176-idf-says-senior-hamas-members-killed-in-al-shifa-operation/0000018e-9055-d9a4-a7bf-dc5d1d7c0000</guid></item><item><title>数千名以色列人加入人质家庭参加大规模集会，警察与反内塔尼亚胡抗议者发生冲突； 16人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/protests-against-netanyahus-govt-in-support-for-hostage-release-break-out-across-israel/0000018e-9000-d229-adae-91d3fb440000</link><description>抗议者封锁了特拉维夫主要高速公路，加沙被扣押人质家属宣布争取人质释放协议的斗争升级，警察和抗议者之间爆发冲突。以色列各地数千人示威反对政府，呼吁提前选举</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 16:10:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/protests-against-netanyahus-govt-in-support-for-hostage-release-break-out-across-israel/0000018e-9000-d229-adae-91d3fb440000</guid></item><item><title>四名联合国工作人员在黎巴嫩联黎部队车辆袭击中受伤；以色列否认参与</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/four-un-staff-wounded-in-unifil-vehicle-strike-in-lebanon-israel-denies-involvement/0000018e-8fb3-def1-a58f-efbb64590000</link><description>联黎部队表示，受伤人员已被疏散接受治疗，目前仍在调查爆炸起因。以色列立即否认参与该事件</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 14:43:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/four-un-staff-wounded-in-unifil-vehicle-strike-in-lebanon-israel-denies-involvement/0000018e-8fb3-def1-a58f